title: 820-3437-B orange light but not turn on
message:
Any pulse at the big coils?
Check if any PM_SLP_Sx_L signal pulses triggering SMC_ONOFF_L.
Did you try to start in SMC bypass mode?
Check for corrosion around U1950 and U6100.

title: 820-3437-B orange light but not turn on
message:
SMC bypass mode start it for few seconds and stop fan spinning.
yes, Pulse at the big coils.

corrosion around U1950 and U6100.Yes.
